name: The Charis Tsevis NFT collection - old

metadata.name: Good luck, Rocket Man!
metadata.description: Elon Musk is one of these guys that really shine bright. He is a man on a mission in so many fields. I have used a neofuturistic, neocubistic approach in the mosaic structure and I have filled my mosaics with photos from the SpaceX activities. SpaceX was one of the very first companies using the No Copyright / Public Domain status.
